267
00:15:04.289 --> 00:15:05.789
Yes, sir.

268
00:15:11.389 --> 00:15:13.189
Inspector.

269
00:15:13.189 --> 00:15:15.589
Do you notice any difference between the two?

270
00:15:15.589 --> 00:15:17.589
No. Not at all.

271
00:15:17.589 --> 00:15:20.789
Let us in!

272
00:15:20.789 --> 00:15:22.589
Wait.

273
00:15:30.989 --> 00:15:33.589
-Okay? -Yes.

274
00:15:39.989 --> 00:15:42.489
Then, the last one, Mr. Ushigome.

275
00:15:42.489 --> 00:15:43.689
Yeah.

276
00:15:43.689 --> 00:15:46.789
I wear this and walk towards you, right?

277
00:15:48.589 --> 00:15:50.489
Mr. Mouri.

278
00:15:50.489 --> 00:15:53.389
I'm sure you have your reasons.

279
00:15:53.389 --> 00:15:56.989
But unless you tell me where and how to look carefully,

280
00:15:56.989 --> 00:15:58.589
I don't have the slightest idea.

281
00:16:10.789 --> 00:16:13.689
Are you okay, mister?

282
00:16:13.689 --> 00:16:14.789
It's me.

283
00:16:14.789 --> 00:16:17.689
It's you, sonny.

284
00:16:17.689 --> 00:16:19.389
I'm fine.

285
00:16:20.889 --> 00:16:24.289
Will this do, Detective?

286
00:16:24.289 --> 00:16:26.889
Yes. I more or less thought it would come out this way,

287
00:16:26.889 --> 00:16:29.789
but now I'm positive.

288
00:16:29.789 --> 00:16:31.489
That Mr. Ushigome...

289
00:16:31.489 --> 00:16:37.089
You're the one who killed Mr. Nagase!

290
00:16:40.389 --> 00:16:42.689
What?

291
00:16:42.689 --> 00:16:44.589
It's the same

292
00:16:44.589 --> 00:16:47.089
as the killer who was in the video.

293
00:16:47.089 --> 00:16:48.489
He kept looking around!

294
00:16:48.489 --> 00:16:50.289
Looking around?

295
00:16:50.289 --> 00:16:51.689
Yes.

296
00:16:51.689 --> 00:16:53.889
You'll find out when you wear it,

297
00:16:53.889 --> 00:16:56.789
but a wrestler's mask has narrower vision than is actually thought to be!

298
00:16:56.789 --> 00:16:59.489
Unless you're used to wearing it,

299
00:16:59.489 --> 00:17:01.789
you tend to look around,

300
00:17:01.789 --> 00:17:04.589
trying to make out the situation of the surroundings

301
00:17:04.589 --> 00:17:06.889
or trip over things that are at your feet

302
00:17:06.889 --> 00:17:09.289
because it is a blind spot.

303
00:17:09.289 --> 00:17:10.789
In other words,

304
00:17:10.789 --> 00:17:14.589
Mr. Ogami who is used to wearing the mask of Wolf Face,

305
00:17:14.589 --> 00:17:18.289
Mr. Rossi who is used to wearing the mask of Nega Wolf

306
00:17:18.289 --> 00:17:22.889
and Mr. Sakuma who usually pitches in for Mr. Ogami.

307
00:17:22.889 --> 00:17:25.889
They have all been ruled out as suspects.

308
00:17:25.889 --> 00:17:31.089
You're the only one who's not used to wearing the mask!

309
00:17:32.789 --> 00:17:34.989
You mean I'm branded killer

310
00:17:34.989 --> 00:17:37.089
just because I looked around and tripped!

311
00:17:37.089 --> 00:17:41.089
The evidence is right there on the videotape!

312
00:17:41.089 --> 00:17:45.789
Remember what Conan said about behind the mask a while ago.

313
00:17:45.789 --> 00:17:48.989
Do you see that extra something?

314
00:17:48.989 --> 00:17:53.389
There are four strings sticking out from behind the mask?

315
00:17:53.389 --> 00:17:54.589
I get it!

316
00:17:54.589 --> 00:17:56.189
The killer was wearing the thin mask

317
00:17:56.189 --> 00:18:00.289
worn when having meals under another mask!

318
00:18:00.289 --> 00:18:01.289
That way,

319
00:18:01.289 --> 00:18:04.089
the hair and eyebrows of the killer won't stick to the inside of the mask

320
00:18:04.089 --> 00:18:07.189
that has the blood splatters!

321
00:18:07.189 --> 00:18:09.089
I see.

322
00:18:09.089 --> 00:18:13.389
That's why although the victim tore half the mask off,

323
00:18:13.389 --> 00:18:14.789
no remnants of skin of the killer

324
00:18:14.789 --> 00:18:17.089
were found in the nails of the victim.

325
00:18:17.089 --> 00:18:20.289
Isn't this the mask for meals that you're talking about?

326
00:18:20.289 --> 00:18:24.589
It was sticking out of your pocket when you fell.

327
00:18:24.589 --> 00:18:26.089
Oh, no.

328
00:18:26.089 --> 00:18:29.889
That's the mask I keep in order to scare the young wrestlers

329
00:18:29.889 --> 00:18:32.489
and not the one that the killer was wearing.

330
00:18:32.489 --> 00:18:34.389
It's strange.

331
00:18:34.389 --> 00:18:37.089
Wolf Face's mask is black and white,

332
00:18:37.089 --> 00:18:40.789
but there's a red spot by the right eye.

333
00:18:40.789 --> 00:18:42.389
Oh, I get it!

334
00:18:42.389 --> 00:18:45.389
The right eye part of the mask that you were wearing on top got ripped

335
00:18:45.389 --> 00:18:47.889
so the blood splattered on here!

336
00:18:47.889 --> 00:18:49.589
You brat.

337
00:18:49.589 --> 00:18:51.889
Okay, that's it!

338
00:18:51.889 --> 00:18:53.589
We'll hear you out at the station.

339
00:18:53.589 --> 00:18:55.689
Shut up!

340
00:18:55.689 --> 00:18:57.289
Hey, Mr. Ushigome?

341
00:18:57.289 --> 00:18:59.189
I'm telling you to shut up!

342
00:19:02.589 --> 00:19:03.889
That's right.

343
00:19:03.889 --> 00:19:05.789
I did it.

344
00:19:07.389 --> 00:19:09.089
I killed the betrayer

345
00:19:09.089 --> 00:19:11.789
who wanted to transfer to the Bankoku Pro Wrestling Team!

346
00:19:11.789 --> 00:19:14.389
Cool it, Mr. Ushigome.

347
00:19:14.389 --> 00:19:16.089
That's not all!

348
00:19:19.189 --> 00:19:22.489
I was going to take the mask away from you by framing you up,

349
00:19:22.489 --> 00:19:25.289
a young wrestler with no name, as the killer!

350
00:19:25.289 --> 00:19:28.489
So that I become Wolf Face!

351
00:19:28.489 --> 00:19:31.389
Didn't you hear a strange sound just now?

352
00:19:33.589 --> 00:19:35.389
Right.

353
00:19:35.389 --> 00:19:37.489
As long as I get to wear this mask I can become...

354
00:19:37.489 --> 00:19:40.089
You can never become the Wolf!

355
00:19:41.789 --> 00:19:43.989
You may be able to hide your face with the mask,

356
00:19:43.989 --> 00:19:47.089
but you can't hide your heart that's full of soot and rotten to the gut,

357
00:19:47.089 --> 00:19:48.889
having no respect for professional wrestling.

358
00:19:54.689 --> 00:19:56.189
Excuse me...

359
00:19:56.189 --> 00:19:57.789
Conan?

360
00:20:02.189 --> 00:20:04.389
Kid, what do you know about me?

361
00:20:04.389 --> 00:20:05.889
Stop it!

362
00:20:25.189 --> 00:20:28.489
Shining Wizard?

363
00:20:28.489 --> 00:20:29.589
Right, that's it!

364
00:20:29.589 --> 00:20:31.789
That's the name of the technique!

365
00:20:31.789 --> 00:20:33.089
I'm glad.

366
00:20:33.089 --> 00:20:35.289
I finally remember the name!

367
00:20:41.289 --> 00:20:42.989
And then after that,

368
00:20:42.989 --> 00:20:44.989
the killer, Mr. Ushigome,

369
00:20:44.989 --> 00:20:47.789
was slapped once in the cheek by a speechless Mr. Kiba.

370
00:20:50.289 --> 00:20:51.989
He was then escorted

371
00:20:51.989 --> 00:20:55.089
from the white mat to a dimly lit jail.

372
00:22:30.289 --> 00:22:34.189
But things are going to get rough for you from now on.

373
00:22:34.189 --> 00:22:37.089
The mass media is going to bash you from now on saying things like

374
00:22:37.089 --> 00:22:39.989
you're a murderous professional wrestler and stuff.

375
00:22:39.989 --> 00:22:41.889
I'll be fine.

376
00:22:42.989 --> 00:22:45.689
We, wrestlers, are tough.

377
00:22:45.689 --> 00:22:47.889
We're used to being bashed and hit.

378
00:22:50.889 --> 00:22:52.489
So, I'll see you all then.

379
00:22:52.489 --> 00:22:55.289
I wish you luck.

380
00:22:55.289 --> 00:22:56.589
Yes.

381
00:22:56.589 --> 00:22:59.289
They're the toughest guys around.

382
00:23:00.989 --> 00:23:04.589
It's no problem for them to overcome difficulties like this.

383
00:23:04.589 --> 00:23:09.189
And, so long as Wolf Face keeps on winning,

384
00:23:09.189 --> 00:23:12.289
his identity will stay undercover.

385
00:23:13.889 --> 00:23:17.489
Then you see, Mr. Ogami from the top rope.

386
00:23:17.489 --> 00:23:18.989
Mr. Ogami?

387
00:23:18.989 --> 00:23:21.289
I thought you were talking about Wolf Face?

388
00:23:23.289 --> 00:23:26.689
So you know wolf! Mr. Wolf! (Ogami is Homonym of Wolf)

389
00:23:26.689 --> 00:23:28.389
Because he's a wolf?

390
00:23:28.389 --> 00:23:31.889
Yes...

391
00:23:31.889 --> 00:23:36.189
Wolf Face's identity will probably

392
00:23:36.189 --> 00:23:39.089
never be revealed.

393
00:23:39.089 --> 00:23:40.589
I think.

